TBy

TBy (Toolboxy) provides a heterogeneous collection of functions and classes.

Contents

Following modules are included:

- CallStack

Gets the current call stack

- ClassHelper

Generic support functions for AHK-classes

- RunOrActivate

Starts a program or activates the program if its already running
